a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ch\u00fat t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0&nbsp;<strong>Tr\u1ea7n Th\u1ea1ch Qu\u1ed1c C\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong>&nbsp;sinh n\u0103m 1989, thu\u1ed9c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a 8X. L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed9i 100% (max level nh\u00e9), v\u00ec v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i m\u00e1y v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kinh doanh, ch\u1eb3ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn blogging. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1 sai \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00ec tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n blog CuongThach \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. Trong 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i dung blog, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1o content nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u201cx\u00e2y n\u1ec1n\u201d \u0111\u00e3 xong.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\" style=\"flex-basis:30%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1821\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Cuong-Profile-5-1-1024x1821.png\" alt=\"Cuong Profile 5 (1)\" class=\"wp-image-19718\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-feature ugb-feature ugb-2dcceb5 ugb-feature--v2 ugb-feature--design-plain ugb-feature--invert ugb-main-block ugb-main-block--inner-center ugb--has-block-background ugb--has-bottom-separator\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-2dcceb5.ugb-feature{background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}.ugb-2dcceb5.ugb-feature:before{background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}.ugb-2dcceb5 .ugb-bottom-separator{transform:scaleX(-1)}.ugb-2dcceb5 .ugb-bottom-separator .ugb-separator__layer-2{fill:#dadada}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.ugb-2dcceb5 .ugb-feature__item{grid-template-columns:0.70fr 1.30fr !important}}<\/style><div class=\"ugb-bottom-separator\"><div class=\"ugb-separator-wrapper\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 1600 200\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"ugb-separator__layer-1\" preserveaspectratio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path class=\"wave-3_svg__st2\" d=\"M1413.6 161.4c-157.9 0-338.2-37.7-495.1-67.4-215.6-40.8-328.1-44.6-418.2-41.1S317 73.4 188.4 102-10 136.2-10 136.2v74.2h1620v-68.5s-68.8 19.5-196.4 19.5z\"><\/path><\/svg><svg viewbox=\"0 0 1600 200\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" preserveaspectratio=\"none\" class=\"ugb-separator__layer-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1292.3 72.5C1081 72.5 649.1 191.4 591 209h1019v-77s-132.4-59.5-317.7-59.5z\"><\/path><\/svg><svg viewbox=\"0 0 1600 200\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" preserveaspectratio=\"none\" class=\"ugb-separator__layer-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M1404 141.9c-177.2-10.3-284-48-440.4-95.9C755.8-17.7 618.9.9 486.7 22 397.4 36.3 317 59.7 188.4 88.3S-10 122.5-10 122.5V208h1620v-79.8s-78.6 21.1-206 13.7z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-feature__item\"><div class=\"ugb-feature__content\"><h2 class=\"ugb-feature__title\">T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i vi\u1ebft blog?<\/h2><p class=\"ugb-feature__description\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n l\u1ea1i n\u00ean vi\u1ebft blog. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n online kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec blog.<br><br>V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, blog s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n l\u1ea1i cho nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 mai sau. Blog th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Blog l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ti\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01af\u1edaC M\u01a0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Blog tho\u1ea3 m\u00e3n \u0111am m\u00ea ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Blog l\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t cho t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do v\u00f9ng v\u1eaby, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 t\u00f4i l\u00e0 con c\u00e1 m\u1eadp th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o b\u1ecb ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.<br><br>Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nghi ng\u1edd b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung t\u00ecm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi khi n\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec th\u00f4i.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"ugb-feature__image-side\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1821\" class=\"ugb-feature__image ugb-img wp-image-17601\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3-1024x1821.png\" alt=\"Cuong Profile 3\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3-218x388.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3-169x300.png 169w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3-394x700.png 394w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/Cuong-Profile-3-768x1366.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"alignfull wp-block-ugb-container ugb-container ugb-container--width-small ugb-d78e896 ugb-container--v2 ugb-container--design-plain ugb-main-block ugb-main-block--inner-center ugb--has-block-background\" id=\"\"><style>.ugb-d78e896 > .ugb-inner-block > .ugb-block-content > *{padding-right:0px !important;padding-left:0px !important}.ugb-d78e896-wrapper > .ugb-container__side{padding-top:35px !important;padding-bottom:35px !important}.ugb-d78e896-wrapper.ugb-container__wrapper{padding-top:0 !important;padding-bottom:0 !important}.ugb-d78e896.ugb-container{margin-top:0px !important;padding-right:0px !important;padding-left:0px !important;background-color:#ffffff}.ugb-d78e896.ugb-container:before{background-color:#ffffff}@media screen and (max-width:768px){.ugb-d78e896.ugb-container{margin-top:0px !important}}<\/style><div class=\"ugb-inner-block\"><div class=\"ugb-block-content\"><div class=\"ugb-container__wrapper ugb-d78e896-wrapper\"><div class=\"ugb-container__side\"><div class=\"ugb-container__content-wrapper ugb-d78e896-content-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-bottom\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\" style=\"flex-basis:70%\">\n<h2>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec \u1edf CuongThach?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1c blogger m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp m\u00f4n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ec h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng kinh t\u1ebf, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng tin, internet v\u00e0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p blogging n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi ng\u00e0nh blogging th\u00ec b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi blog CuongThach v\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u201cv\u00e0ng\u201d gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Song song \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng blog. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 th\u1ee9c \u0103n \u201ctri th\u1ee9c\u201d m\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Ngon tuy\u1ec7t!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\" style=\"flex-basis:30%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"577\" height=\"433\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Cuong-Tran.png\" alt=\"Cuong Tran\" class=\"wp-image-19738\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Cuong-Tran.png 577w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Cuong-Tran-218x164.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Cuong-Tran-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":18474,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","